metadata.name: Doodle King #1
metadata.description: PUBLIC MINT is Live: https://www.doodlekingclub.com. A Movement of the NFT community led by proud Doodle members. Become a Doodle. As an Doodle King Club member, you can own any of the 6,969 Doodles, thoughtfully recreated into unique AI-generated Doodle King Paintings. Only one painting will be minted for each King, and 24 distinct AI-models have been applied across the collection, to help create value for the owner of every individual ERC-721 token.
